chav1961.purelib.i18n

Interface LocalizerFactory.FillLocalizedContentCallback<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the object instance (see LocalizerFactory.buildLocalizerForInstance(Object) for details)
    Enclosing class:
    LocalizerFactory
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public static interface LocalizerFactory.FillLocalizedContentCallback<T>

    This lambda-styled interface describes callback for storing localized data thru LocaleSpecificTextSetter interface.

    Since:
    0.0.2
    Author:
    Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961

        Fill the given field thru LocaleSpecificTextSetter interface

        Parameters:
        localizer - current localizer
        instance - object instance to fill it's field (see LocalizerFactory.buildLocalizerForInstance(Object))
        f - field description to fill
        text - value to fill text
        tooltip - value to fill tooltip
        toFill - field value to fill
        postprocess - callback to modify localized string before assign it to target
